#: ../../source/guides/localization.rst:2 005f4c511e3741f6a14697e2a34e3ae8
msgid "Localization"
msgstr "本地化"

#: ../../source/guides/localization.rst:4 ac00aa7d837045c9a357f1d32f5c9de8
msgid ""
"Stacklands has a built-in localization system in the form of the "
"``SokLoc`` class, the source code of which can be found in ``SokLoc."
"dll``. You should use localization for your mod even if you only provide "
"translations for a single language, because other modders can easily "
"create translation mods for yours."
msgstr ""
"堆叠大陆有一个内置本地化系统 ``SokLoc`` 类，其源代码可以在 ``SokLoc."
"dll`` 中找到。即使你只提供单一语言的翻译，你也应该为你的模组使用本地化，"
"这样其他模组可以很容易地为你的模组创建翻译模组。"

#: ../../source/guides/localization.rst:10 12e95ee58315438fb35596de7b8095f4
msgid "Creating your localization document"
msgstr "创建你的本地化文档"

#: ../../source/guides/localization.rst:12 6bdb3a78e2c14940b967f15ce41f5756
msgid ""
"Localization documents are in `TSV format <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Tab-separated_values>`_, which you can easily create using Google Sheets "
"or Excel."
msgstr ""
"本地化文档使用 `TSV 格式 <https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tab-"
"separated_values>`_, 你可以使用谷歌表格或 Excel 轻松创建。"

#: ../../source/guides/localization.rst:15 9b8cebbfed074fb0aa10d1b16d6cf0c7
msgid "The first row of the document should look like this:"
msgstr "文档的第一行应该像这样："

#: ../../source/guides/localization.rst:23 a4de669f950a41fba0b38707302a9572
msgid ""
"You do not need to make columns for languages you don't provide "
"translations for! They will automatically fall back to the English "
"column."
msgstr "无需为不提供翻译的语言设置栏目！它们会自动回落到英文栏。"

#: ../../source/guides/localization.rst:25 1e04ead342f34607a5a09186eb386e6e
msgid ""
"Make sure your terms are unique, prefixing them with your mod's ID is an "
"easy way to ensure this."
msgstr "确保你的本地化键是唯一的，使用模组 ID 作为前缀是一种简单的方法。"

#: ../../source/guides/localization.rst:30 2e364796add2414eb85912ff4f7305e7
msgid "Loading your localization document into the game"
msgstr "在游戏中加载你的本地化文档"

