#: ../../source/guides/localization.rst:45 d87790d742e342c1bedc93d73833fb48
msgid "Using SokLoc"
msgstr "使用 ``SokLoc``"

#: ../../source/guides/localization.rst:47 d26189c6ecd845378dd37e486899ac93
msgid "To get a translated string, use the ``SokLoc.Translate`` method:"
msgstr "为了获取一个已经翻译过的字符串，使用 ``SokLoc.Translate`` 方法："

#: ../../source/guides/localization.rst:57 3db73ab051f246f0906801d1982a0c05
msgid "Using LocParams"
msgstr "使用 ``LocParams``"

#: ../../source/guides/localization.rst:59 1f5f7e1c760f4f13bcc710546dececcb
msgid ""
"The localization system provides a very easy way to handle variables in "
"strings. By surrounding text with ``[]``, it's handled as a variable. "
"Example: ``wow, an [epic_param]!``."
msgstr ""
"本地化系统提供了一种非常简单的方法来处理字符串中的变量。用 ``[]`` 包围文"
"本，就能将其作为变量处理。例如：``wow, an [epic_param]!``。"

#: ../../source/guides/localization.rst:70 3ab24a42c7df4bd89049de8d0e5f2c8a
msgid "Using plurals"
msgstr "使用复数形式"

#: ../../source/guides/localization.rst:72 4ac8602a67d5429181c1cd606b73e3ab
msgid ""
"The localization system provides an easy way to handle cases where a "
"string should be translated differently based on a variable number. You "
"can separate the singular and plural forms by prefixing them with "
"``<one>`` and ``<other>``. Example: ``<one>give me one more "
"coin<other>give me [count] more coins``."
msgstr ""
"本地化系统提供了一种简便的方法来处理根据可变数字对字符串进行不同翻译的情"
"况。您可以用 ``<one>`` 和 ``<other>`` 分开单数和复数形式。例如： "
"``<one>give me one more coin<other>give me [count] more coins``。"

#: ../../source/guides/localization.rst:83 1e01f25048ff43c2829e71222c35dd30
msgid "Exporting your document in TSV format"
msgstr "将你的文档导出为 TSV 格式"

#: ../../source/guides/localization.rst:86 85be1e9ae46c4f678e6e0444850172ae
msgid "Excel"
msgstr "Excel"

#: ../../source/guides/localization.rst:88 c4ce7f3816c74228800ee67cf8265b9e
msgid ""
"``File > Save As`` and select ``Tab Separated Value (.txt)`` as the "
"format."
msgstr ""
"``文件 > 另存为`` 然后选择 ``文本文件(制表符分隔)(*.txt)`` 作为格式（不同"
"版本可能有出入）。"

#: ../../source/guides/localization.rst:91 af29149f16ba443dae725e6721fe00d1
msgid "Don't forget to change the file extension to ``.tsv``!"
msgstr "不要忘了将文件拓展名更改为 ``.tsv``！"

#: ../../source/guides/localization.rst:94 f01974efc215440f8c3d4608b98a0524
msgid ""
"Excel may add an empty line to the end of the file, which can cause "
"Stacklands to parse it improperly. If this is the case, simply remove "
"the last empty line in the file."
msgstr ""
"Excel 可能会在文件末尾添加空行，这可能会导致游戏解析错误。如果出现这种情"
"况，只需删除文件中的最后一行空行即可。"

#: ../../source/guides/localization.rst:97 4e5d6da362244758b94cffbd83466d9f
msgid "Google Sheets"
msgstr "谷歌表格"

#: ../../source/guides/localization.rst:99 94816ccee74a459c9706742e4aceaf90
msgid "``File > Download > Tab Seperated values (.tsv)``."
msgstr "``文件 > 下载 > 文本文件(制表符分隔)(.tsv)``。"
